::Diamomd::

She came around enough to hear him say that he was high up in the 
ranks and sticking with him would be good.  She groaned and opened 
her eyes. She looked at him and saw three of him.  She thought that 
her head must have been hit hard. She sighed and closed her eyes, 
hoping the growning head ahce that she had would stop soon. "So your 
high up huh? wha..." She winced as her head felt like it was hit with 
a grenade.  "What are you going to do with me?" She leaned against 
his shoulder and hoped her head would stop hurting. "And where are we 
going?"
